(44, 5, 32, 44, 1, 8, 8, NULL, 'Witnesses and the Holy Ghost', 'Both passages emphasize the role of witnesses and the Holy Ghost. Acts 5:32 mentions being witnesses alongside the Holy Ghost, while Acts 1:8 highlights receiving power from the Holy Ghost to be witnesses.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
